node.text:
@jeffmackdesigns is an entrepreneur that we truly admire here at @archdose. The main goal of his company is to create custom built furniture, with a combination of wood and epoxy finish, designed to last a life time! He built is empire from the ground up and has now a community of over 700,000 people.
Give us your thoughts on one of his personal favorites! 👇

WOOD: Maple
EPOXY: @ecopoxy FlowCast
PIGMENT: @ecopoxy Caviar
FORM MATERIAL: HDPE (High Density Polyethylene) and plywood with our Form Building Tape. We seal our forms with @akfixna Silicone.
SANDER/BUFFER: @gemindustriesinc 11” sander/buffer.
FINISH: @rubiomonocoatusa Pure 2C Oil.
-
Shop these supplies and more at www.JeffMackSupply.com.
-
Get a quote on a custom built table at www.JeffMackDesigns.com
